&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee system performance, stability and uptime&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Automate the environment and test new technology fads&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Architect, implement, maintain and monitor our rapidly growing US production environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage applications in production, and monitor their behavior&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Address potential failures and bottlenecks to proactively prevent obstacles&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Requirements:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience managing mission-critical infrastructure and software support (in a trading environment is a plus)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Intimate knowledge of networking, hardware and OSs (Windows, Linux)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiar with tooling and best practices regarding change, life cycle and incident management, as well as health and performance monitoring of production systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficient with scripting (e.g., bash, python)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Quick at analyzing issues and uncovering their root causes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Eager to learn and understand all aspects of the trading environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to spot inefficiencies and proactive in optimizing systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong communications skills, including the ability to effectively communicate technical information to a non-technical audience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
